text.tspan: We are 95% confident that the proportion of binge drinkers is between 7.0%
and 4.5% higher in male students than in female students.
A survey of 17,096 students in US four-year colleges collected information about
drinking behaviour and alcohol-related problems. Numbers of male and female
'binge-drinkers' (5+ drinks 3 or more times in the past 2 weeks) are shown below.
